trans-unit.source: Specifies a custom class that extends the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> class for use by Web Part connections.
trans-unit.target: Angir en egendefinert klasse som utvider den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> klasse for bruk av webdel-tilkoblinger.

trans-unit.source: TransformerInfo objects specify custom classes that extend the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> class.
trans-unit.target: TransformerInfo objekter angi egendefinerte klasser som utvider <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer>

trans-unit.source: These custom transformer classes act as bridges between Web Parts, translating data between Web Parts with incompatible connection points.
trans-unit.target: Disse egendefinerte transformeringen klassene fungere som broer mellom webdeler oversette data mellom webdeler med inkompatible tilkoblingen punkt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> class with the specified name and type reference.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"> </xref> klassen med den angitte referansen for navn og type.

trans-unit.source: The configuration system does not validate the specified type to ensure that a valid type name is used.
trans-unit.target: Konfigurasjonssystemet validere ikke den angitte typen for å sikre at et gyldig typenavn brukes.

trans-unit.source: The name of this transformer type.
A reference to a type that extends the transformer <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: En referanse til en type som utvider transformeringen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Compares the current <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> object to another <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligner gjeldende <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"> </xref> objekt til et annet <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.TransformerInfo"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare to the current object.
trans-unit.target: Objektet til å sammenligne gjeldende objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the passed object is equal to the current object; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis det angitte objektet er lik det gjeldende objektet. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Generates a hash code for the collection.
Unique integer hash code for the current object.
trans-unit.target: Unikt heltall hash-kode for det gjeldende objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a friendly name for a type that that extends the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et egendefinert navn for en type som utvider den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.target: Konfigurasjonssystemet validere ikke den angitte typen for å sikre at et gyldig typenavn brukes.

trans-unit.source: However, invalid types will cause exceptions when Web pages are loaded.
trans-unit.target: Ugyldig typer fører imidlertid unntak når nettsider er lastet inn.
